â€œThis strain in concentrate form tastes very earthy and has a hash like resin taste at the end. Concentrate was shatter and it was taken with a large snake like dab. It delivers a hell of an Indica effect to it, it's alright.â€

â€œCerebral, and relaxing good for evening use. I had two bowls after work, and felt relaxed and euphoric. â€œFound a frosty fruity berry pheno with no herms after 3 rounds. Great OG funk under the sweetness and all OG on exhale. Great mid-end of day smoke to get the stress moving out.â€

â€œVery cerebral, and relaxing great for night time smoke seshes. I felt fairly immediate body relaxation, and euphoria.
